    "bodyHtml": "<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Explore a curated portfolio of commercial films, cinematic brand campaigns, and product launch videos produced by Vantage Pictures for global clients. We specialize in helping Asian technology brands — particularly from China — connect with Western audiences through internationally positioned campaigns, while also delivering high-end commercial storytelling across automotive, energy, lifestyle, and documentary-driven brand films worldwide.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->",
