  {
    "wpId": 3072,
    "title": "Vietnam Location Guidebook",
    "titleZh": "越南取景地指南",
    "slug": "vietnam-location-guide",
    "slugZh": "越南旅游指南",
    "showHeroHeader": true,
    "heroTitle": "<span class=\"vp-outline\">Vietnam</span> Location Guidebook",
    "featuredImageWpId": 3074,
    "bodyHtml": "<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row {\"template\":\"custom\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Row (10-Column Centered)\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column {\"sizeSm\":10,\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"col-sm-10\"},\"className\":\"offset-sm-1\"} -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vietnam <span class=\"vp-outline\">Filming Location Guide</span></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Download our Vietnam Location Guide, a curated production resource designed for international agencies, producers, and commercial film teams planning shoots across the country. This guide highlights diverse filming locations in Vietnam — from modern cityscapes and industrial zones to tropical coastlines, mountain landscapes, and remote natural environments — helping you evaluate creative possibilities before your production begins.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Created by the team at Vantage Pictures, the guide reflects real-world production experience supporting global commercial shoots throughout Vietnam.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {\"id\":3075,\"href\":\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Vietnam_Location_Guide_Vantage_Pictures.pdf\",\"displayPreview\":false} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-35f31319-a88b-43a7-bf99-b845e28e130b\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Vietnam_Location_Guide_Vantage_Pictures.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Vietnam_Location_Guide_Vantage_Pictures.pdf</a><a href=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Vietnam_Location_Guide_Vantage_Pictures.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button wp-element-button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-35f31319-a88b-43a7-bf99-b845e28e130b\">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->",
    "noIndex": false,
    "seo": {
      "metaDescription": "Download our Vietnam filming location guide featuring diverse commercial shoot locations and production insights for international crews.",
