  {
    "wpId": 3794,
    "title": "Vietnam Production Service",
    "titleZh": "<a aria-current=\"page\" title=\"越南制作服务\" role=\"menuitem\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/zh/越南生产服务/\" class=\"dropdown-item active\">越南制作服务</a>",
    "slug": "vietnam-production-service",
    "slugZh": "越南生产服务",
    "showHeroHeader": true,
    "heroTitle": "Vietnam <span class=\"vp-outline\">Production Service</span>",
    "heroTitleZh": "越南制作服务",
    "featuredImageWpId": 2480,
    "bodyHtml": "<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row {\"template\":\"custom\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Row (10-Column Centered)\"},\"className\":\"mt-4\"} -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column {\"sizeSm\":10,\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"col-sm-10\"},\"className\":\"offset-sm-1\"} -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vietnam Production Service <span class=\"vp-outline\">for International Commercial Shoots</span></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vantage Pictures provides full-service Vietnam production support for international brands, agencies, and production companies shooting commercials, brand films, documentaries, and product campaigns across the country. With extensive experience servicing global clients, we deliver reliable local execution with international production standards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Film in Vietnam?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vietnam offers diverse landscapes, competitive production costs, skilled local crews, and streamlined logistics for international commercial shoots. From modern cityscapes in Ho Chi Minh City and Hanoi to tropical coastlines, mountain ranges, and industrial environments, Vietnam provides a wide range of visually distinctive locations within close geographic proximity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"columns\":4,\"imageCrop\":false,\"linkTo\":\"none\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"className\":\"is-style-vp-masonry\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-4 is-style-vp-masonry\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":80,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/son-doong-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Sunlight pouring into Son Doong Cave in Quang Binh, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-80\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Son Doong Cave Quang Binh</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":79,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/saigon-post-office.jpg\" alt=\"The historic Saigon Central Post Office in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-79\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Saigon Central Post Office Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":67,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/da-lat-farm.jpg\" alt=\"Beautiful fields and greenhouses during sunrise at Hasfarm in Da Lat, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-67\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hasfarm Da Lat</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":73,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/hoi-an.jpg\" alt=\"Colorfully lit streets at night in Hoi An, Quang Nam, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-73\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hoi An Quang Nam</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":68,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/golden-bridge.jpg\" alt=\"Tourists crowding Golden Bridge in Da Nang, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-68\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Golden Bridge Da Nang</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":66,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bitexco-financial-tower.jpg\" alt=\"Bitexco Financial Tower at sunset in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-66\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bitexco Financial Tower Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":72,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ho-chi-minh-city-district-1.jpg\" alt=\"Saigon River skyline at night in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-72\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Saigon River Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":82,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tay-ho-pagoda.jpg\" alt=\"Tay Ho Pagoda at sunset in Hanoi, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-82\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Tay Ho Pagoda Hanoi</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":74,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/khau-pha-pass.jpg\" alt=\"Picturesque rice paddies at Khau Pha Pass in Yen Bai, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-74\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Khau Pha Pass Yen Bai</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":78,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/phu-quoc-island.jpg\" alt=\"Beautiful tropical beaches on Phu Quoc Island in Kien Giang, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-78\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Phu Quoc Island Kien Giang</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":81,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tan-dinh-catholic-church.jpg\" alt=\"Pink church Tan Dinh Catholic Church in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-81\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Tan Dinh Catholic Church Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":83,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/thien-hau-temple-incense.jpg\" alt=\"Woman praying with incense at Thien Hau Temple in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-83\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Thien Hau Temple Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":69,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ha-long-bay.jpg\" alt=\"Cruise boats tour the karsts of Ha Long Bay in Quang Ninh, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-69\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Ha Long Bay Quang Ninh</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":71,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/hanoi-skyline.jpg\" alt=\"Hanoi skyline at sunset, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-71\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hanoi</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":76,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/long-bien-bridge.jpg\" alt=\"Boat paddles at sunrise beneath Long Bien Bridge in Hanoi, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-76\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Long Bien Bridge Hanoi</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":75,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/kien-giang.jpg\" alt=\"Rice fields at sunrise in the Mekong Delta, Kien Giang, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-75\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Mekong Delta Kien Giang</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":77,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/national-museum-of-vietnamese-history.jpg\" alt=\"National Museum of Vietnamese History in Hanoi, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-77\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">National Museum of Vietnamese History Hanoi</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":70,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/hang-mua-ninh-binh.jpg\" alt=\"Stairs winding up a jagged Hang Mua Peak in Ninh Binh, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-70\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hang Mua Peak Ninh Binh</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row {\"template\":\"custom\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Row (10-Column Centered)\"},\"className\":\"mt-2 mb-4\"} -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column {\"sizeSm\":10,\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"col-sm-10\"},\"className\":\"offset-sm-1\"} -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Full-Service Production Support&nbsp;<span class=\"vp-outline\">in Vietnam</span></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our Vietnam production services cover every stage of the filmmaking process, including location scouting, permitting, casting, crew sourcing, equipment rental, production management, line producing, budgeting, and post-production coordination. Whether servicing large-scale commercial productions or agile documentary crews, we ensure efficient execution, clear communication, and professional oversight throughout.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Filming Locations&nbsp;<span class=\"vp-outline\">Across Vietnam</span></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our Vietnam production services cover every stage of the filmmaking process, including location scouting, permitting, casting, crew sourcing, equipment rental, production management, line producing, budgeting, and post-production coordination. Whether servicing large-scale commercial productions or agile documentary crews, we ensure efficient execution, clear communication, and professional oversight throughout.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/button {\"url\":\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/vietnam-location-guide/\",\"text\":\"Vietnam Location Guidebook\"} /-->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"columns\":3,\"imageCrop\":false,\"linkTo\":\"none\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"className\":\"is-style-vp-masonry\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-3 is-style-vp-masonry\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":61,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/long-island-film-studio.jpg\" alt=\"Long Island Film Studio plot for photography and filming in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-61\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Long Island Film Studio Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":65,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/vaib-production-house.jpg\" alt=\"VAIB studio for photography and filming in Ho Ch Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-65\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">VAIB Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":63,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/starVN.jpg\" alt=\"StarVN studio for filming in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-63\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">StarVN Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":2948,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/89030086_555000368699825_3412428216197971968_n.jpeg\" alt=\"G-Floor Sound Stage at Capital Studio in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-2948\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Capital Studio Vietnam</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":62,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/ps-vietnam.jpg\" alt=\"PS Vietnam rental house for video production in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-62\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">PS Vietnam Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":64,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/vantage-local/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tak17.jpg\" alt=\"Tak17 lighting studio for filming in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam\" class=\"wp-image-64\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Tak17 Ho Chi Minh City</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row {\"template\":\"custom\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Row (10-Column Centered)\"},\"className\":\"mt-4\"} -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column {\"sizeSm\":10,\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"col-sm-10\"},\"className\":\"offset-sm-1\"} -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"vp-outline\">Trusted by</span> Global Brands and Agencies</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We regularly collaborate with international creative teams from Asia, Europe, and North America, supporting cross-border productions with bilingual production management and transparent budgeting. Our experience working with technology brands, consumer electronics companies, and global marketing agencies ensures smooth integration between local Vietnamese crews and international stakeholders.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Shot in <span class=\"vp-outline\">Vietnam</span></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:vp/portfolio-gallery {\"taxonomy\":\"market\",\"terms\":\"vietnam\",\"cols\":3,\"gutter\":3} /-->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row {\"template\":\"custom\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Row (8-Column Centered)\"}} -->\n<!-- wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column {\"sizeMd\":8,\"sizeSm\":10,\"lock\":{\"move\":false,\"remove\":false},\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"col-md-8\"},\"className\":\"offset-md-2 offset-sm-1\"} -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Plan Your Next Production&nbsp;<span class=\"vp-outline\">in Vietnam</span></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you are planning a commercial shoot, brand film, or documentary in Vietnam, contact Vantage Pictures to discuss your project requirements. Our team will provide detailed production guidance, budgeting support, and on-the-ground expertise tailored to your timeline and objectives.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/column -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/row -->\n<!-- /wp:wp-bootstrap-blocks/container -->",
